Create a html page called "ProductDetails.component.html"

The page should have product details designed in bootstrap as shown below:

Copy paste the product.component.html code in this.

Remove all the content inside, the <div id="myContent"> ....

And here do the following:

Add this...

<div class="container">
<div class="row">

  
 
</div>
</div>

Inside the "row" div above, create two columns.
First column should be width 4 units. [Hint: col-md-4]
Second column should be width 8 units.


Now in the first column, we will add a image.
Use this link to add a image/ figure
https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.1/content/figures/

Select your own image from google. Search for an abstract image of width 400x300 
--------------

In the second column....

Use this link 
https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.1/content/typography/

to create,
heading H1 with text "Product Name"

Below this copy, paste the below code

<div class="row">
<div class="col-2">
<label>Price: </label>
</div>
<div class="col-10">
$
</div>
</div>

<div class="row">
<div class="col-2">
