PART 2 of the assignment.

Create another typescript file called 
product.ts

Copy-paste the sampletype.ts in it. 
---------------------------------

You saw how to display sampletype.ts data in index.html

Can you do the same thing and make product content display in product.component.html page using product.ts file ? 
Use the second column, yellow cell, to show the data. 

The compilation command is (example)
tsc product.ts


